 <name>elektroid</name>
 <summary>Sample and MIDI device manager</summary>
 <description>
  <p>Elektroid is a sample and MIDI device manager.</p>
  <p>With Elektroid you can easily upload and download audio files and manage different types of data on different MIDI devices, such as presets, projects or tunings.</p>
  <p>It can also be used to send and receive SysEx MIDI files.</p>
 </description>
